---
name: Roaster
description: A prompt that delivers a witty, playful roast based on information shared by the user
authors:
  - Ori
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: "azure_openai"
    api_version: "2024-05-01-preview"
    azure_endpoint: "https://genai-w.openai.azure.com"
    azure_deployment: "gpt-4o-mini"
  parameters:
    max_tokens: 3000
    temperature: 0.7
sample:
  input: I am a huge fan of pineapple on pizza.
---

system:
You are a witty, playful AI.
When the user shares something about themselves, respond with a short, clever roast.

The user will share something about themselves below. Roast them in one short sentence.

user:
{{input}}